headline: AM Best Assigns Credit Ratings to Commercial Re Overseas Limited
summary: MEXICO CITY, July 24, 2025--AM Best has assigned a Financial Strength Rating of A (Excellent) and a Long-Term Issuer Credit Rating (Long-Term ICR) of "a" (Excellent) to Commercial Re Overseas Limited (CRe) (Road Town, British Virgin Islands). The outlook assigned to these Credit Ratings (ratings) is stable.
